<br>
FGs and VS - NO change to FFA .. FCFS is how it should be.<br>
FFA means while you are buffing to take him out right outside his room another group or two can run down and CHARGE him leaving you there casting your last few buffs on 1 or 2 tanks.<br>
<br>
I do not advocate in any way shape or form FFA. I do believe in limits on how long you can claim first come. If you are sitting at the seb zoneline claiming chef asking for a cleric and a a chanter/bard for an hour .. you have no claim to FCFS of that camp. But if you are there fully grouped and just moving in it would be wrong IMHO for another party to come in and take what you were getting prepped for. <p><a href=http://www.etherealknighthood.com border=0><img src=http://home.kscable.com/ethereal/azzisig.gif></a><br><center>
